<br>
I think back when they did the Bertox story and had the Qeynos Badge quests, they didn't implement all the badges at once, but the NPCs that gave the quests didn't talk about parts of it that weren't implemented. That seemed fair, because when they DID implement the quest, the NPC's text changed.<br>
<br>
It just seems really unfair to me that the only thing they've officially said about this is that the spell quest was &quot;working as intended&quot; before they had even injected a single &quot;extraction&quot; combine.<br>
<br>
I have only done bits and pieces of the quest myself, but I'm probably going to wait until something solid happens and is posted here before I keep trying combines myself.<br>
