<br>
The only real way they can test new content is through the test server and I don't know anyone willing to spend the time to get to the required level to be able to actually do some of this stuff. Therefore the test server doesn't really have a lot of testers compared to the live servers.<br>
<br>
I spent a lot of time going about collecting runes, words and pages etc. etc. and then another load of time trying combines to find that every combined resulted in DNC.<br>
<br>
Either they plain forgot to put parts of it in, they put broken content in OR they delibarately missed out content. It doesn't really matter which of these it is because they are slowly but surely fixing it now. Ok, the 44th level word/rune combine still doesn't work but hopefully soon.<br>
<br>
As for not being able to move forward in 30 pages of posts. That is not strictly true. Currently we all know that we can combine certain spells to make notes, we can combine words and runes to make runes and we can combine certain items in the box to extract bindings. This is what I call forward progress.<br>
<br>
It is quite possible that :-<br>
A) The final combines arn't currently in game.<br>
B) The final combines do not currently work as intended.<br>
C) The final combines ARE in game but no one has quite worked out exactly what you need to combine.<br>
<br>
My personal thoughts on this are that you need to combine one binding, one rune and one note to make a spell. I've read here and on Graffe's that people have already tried quite a few of these combines and all came out as DNC but the same thing happened with the rune/word combine. It is quite possible that these combines still arn't in but will be soon. Hell, there was a patch today so they might already be in.<br>
<br>
Personally I'm glad to do these quests, it at least breaks the monoteny of exp grinding or raiding to try and do some brain work and find a solution to a series of quests that don't require raid or uber level forces to complete.<br>
<br>
Wabbus<br>
