This SHOULD be the way it works on the internal test servers, where the public would not get spoilers. The whole &quot;live test server&quot; is a joke and a wash. What they NEED to do is hire competent damned QA testers and pay them a decent enough salary that they actually CARE about doing a good job. One can only guess at how people are treated at VI/SOE, but I imagine it's like any other large company...Peons get shat upon. And because the company is making money and continues to see it's subscriber base grow, they WILL NOT CHANGE. <br>
<br>
Face the music. Unless the head of the company has an epiphany and realizes that their anchor game is buggy and decides to put quality over quantity, they WILL NOT CHANGE. A company's ethic trickles from the top down. SOE's ethic is about making money, not about making money WHILE AT THE SAME TIME making quality product.<br>
